Package: tomo
Version: 1.0.0-1
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: python3 (>= 3.11), python3-venv, python3-pip, nginx, nodejs (>= 18)
Recommends: sqlite3, certbot, python3-certbot-nginx
Maintainer: Christophe Babilotte <christophe@babilotte.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/cbabil/tomo
Description: Self-hosted infrastructure management platform
 Tomo is a web-based platform for managing
 self-hosted infrastructure including:
  - Server management and monitoring
  - Docker container orchestration
  - Application marketplace
  - Automated agent deployment
  - Backup and restore functionality
 .
 This package includes the backend API server, web frontend,
 and CLI administration tool.
